      <title>津巴布韦央行不顾降息要求维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/zimbabwe-s-central-bank-holds-interest-rate-ignoring-pleas-for-a-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦央行在今年第一次会议上将基准利率维持在 35%，无视业界要求其采取宽松立场的请求。]]></description>
