      <title>赢得债券持有人支持后，厄瓜多尔总统寻求选民支持连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/ecuador-holds-presidential-election-with-noboa-in-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹尼尔·诺沃亚成为厄瓜多尔历史上最年轻的总统时，曾承诺要以紧迫感应对双重犯罪和财政危机。然而，他最大的胜利可能是华尔街。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/ecuador-holds-presidential-election-with-noboa-in-lead</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥央行或因经济增长和通胀放缓而加速降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/banxico-may-accelerate-cuts-as-growth-inflation-slow-day-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行周四可能会将货币政策宽松步伐提高一倍，将利率下调半个百分点，使通胀回到目标区间，经济增长放缓，并推迟征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/banxico-may-accelerate-cuts-as-growth-inflation-slow-day-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
